({{nasdaq|GOOG}}) is a [[United States|U.S.]] [[public corporation]], first [[Incorporation|incorporated]] as a [[Private company|privately held corporation]] in [[September]], [[1998]], that designs and manages the Internet [[Google search]] engine.
